videos.description: Tae Hayes comes up with the interception off Tyler Rogers and returns it 52 yards, which leads to an Appalachian State field goal.
videos.headline: Hayes with the interception and returns it 52- yards the other way

videos.description: Clifton Duck jumps the route to make an interception and set up Appalachian State in the red zone.
videos.headline: Duck jumps route for int

videos.description: Jalin Moore squeezes through for a short 3-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Moore finds the end zone for Appalachian State

videos.description: Tyler Rogers throws his third interception of the first half  and his second to Tae Hayes.
videos.headline: Hayes picks off Rogers for second time

videos.description: Terrence Upshaw blasts up the middle for a 13-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Upshaw bursts through the line for 13-yard TD

videos.description: Jaden Wright makes a  heads up interception off of Taylor Lamb.
videos.headline: Wright comes up with the interception for New Mexico State

videos.description: Jason Huntley cuts up  the sideline and jets past defenders for a 48-yard run.
videos.headline: Huntley accelerates for 48-yard gain

videos.description: Jaden Wright comes up with his second interception of the day.
videos.headline: Wright makes key INT

videos.description: Larry Rose III gives New Mexico State the lead on a 1-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Rose marches in for 1-yard TD

videos.description: Tae Hayes makes a key play to give Appalachian State it's fourth interception of the day.
videos.headline: Hayes comes up with the crucial INT

videos.description: Taylor Lamb zips through the hole for a 38-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Lamb calls his own number for 38-yard TD run

videos.description: Tyler Rogers finds Jason Huntley who takes it the distance for a 61-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Huntley shows off his speed with a 61-yard TD

videos.headline: Upshaw cuts in for 10-yard TD run

videos.headline: Appalachian State's Williams uses backwards pass for 27-yard TD

videos.headline: Moore turns on the jets for 56-yard TD
